    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p> And then came the best on -board staff ever. The flight attendant opened his announcement with "Boarding Completed ... I think" - we all had to laugh. He was relaxed all the time, entertaining, warm - just great. We sat at the forefront, got into conversation, and so the long flight time fell almost like in a flash. Particularly nice: from above we could even see the thick clouds above the bubbling volcano on La Palma. Impressive - and a bit surreal. </p>
        <p> And so this nice October vacation came to an end. With lots of sun on your face, sand under your feet, bananas in the stomach and a little volcanic air in your nose. Tired, but happy. </p>
